DataElement.preferredName: Protocol Agent Transfer Administration Performed Study Activity Duration ISO21090.PQ.TIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The completed action in which an authorized party at a designated study site dispenses or receives a study agent to/from a study subject. EXAMPLE(S): Study subject receives a bottle of pills. NOTE(S): The term "study agent" only pertains within the context of a given study. The period of time over which the activity is performed.
